Package: template.dashboard
Type: Package
Title: Boilerplate for 'tidylab' Dashboards
URL: https://tidylab.github.io/template.dashboard/
BugReports: https://github.com/tidylab/template.dashboard/issues
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2020-01-01
Authors@R: c(person("Harel", "Lustiger", email = "tidylab@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Harel Lustiger <tidylab@gmail.com>
Description: Preconfigured dashboard that supports continuous development and 
    deployment of a Shiny application. Committing to master branch triggers:  
    * Dashboard deployment to https://www.shinyapps.io/ (via `rsconnect`); and  
    * Package website deployment (via `pkgdown`).
